     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA07d197n2-ptr" id="PJA07d197n2">2</a>
      <p>Presumably <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> means Hutchinson and his followers.</p>
     </div>
